    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I've used raycat plugin&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.raycast.com/gdsmith/jwt-decoder" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://www.raycast.com/gdsmith/jwt-decoder&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;to decode JWT token&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Also, I never say "jot," but instead spell it as J-W-T. Thankfully, I'm not the only one who does this -&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D2D9umQMKhA" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D2D9umQMKhA&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/application-development-discussions/sap-developer-challenge-apis-task-11-examine-the-access-token-for-scopes/m-p/282374#M3690"/>
    <published>2023-08-28T08:38:32.470000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/application-development-discussions/sap-developer-challenge-apis-task-11-examine-the-access-token-for-scopes/m-p/282575#M3735</id>
    <title>Re: SAP Developer Challenge - APIs - Task 11 - Examine the access token for scopes contained</title>
    <updated>2023-08-28T15:37:29.299000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>seVladimirs</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/312</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P class=""&gt;The grant_type specified is incorrect. Please refer to &lt;A href="https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/application-development/sap-developer-challenge-apis-task-10-request-an-oauth-access/m-p/281933" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/application-development/sap-developer-challenge-apis-task-10-request-an-oauth-access/m-p/281933&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt; which states that the ‘client_credentials’ type cannot be used for this exercise.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/application-development-discussions/sap-developer-challenge-apis-task-11-examine-the-access-token-for-scopes/m-p/282575#M3735"/>
    <published>2023-08-28T15:37:29.299000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
